<p>Each element of this kit, including the hypoallergenic microporous adhesive tape, is carefully packaged to maintain its sterility and effectiveness. The product complies with CE standards, ensuring its adherence to international quality standards. This kit is presented in a compact and ergonomic form, facilitating its transport and practical use in all emergency circumstances.</p>

