py-2">Compliance</td> <td class="border-b-2 border-gray-200 py-2">CE Certification</td> </tr> <tr> <td class="border-b-2 border-gray-200 py-2">Clinical Use</td> <td class="border-b-2 border-gray-200 py-2">Selective pulmonary intubation</td> </tr> <tr> <td class="border-b-2 border-gray-200 py-2">Features</td> <td class="border-b-2 border-gray-200 py-2">Beveled, atraumatic tip</td> </tr> </tbody> </table>' WHERE id = 41;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Fast Track Laryngeal Mask (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The <strong>Fast Track Laryngeal Mask</strong>, SKU identifier LMA135130, is a highly sophisticated medical device intended for single-use professional application. Made from high-quality <em>medical-grade silicone</em>, this mask is designed to ensure optimal biocompatibility while providing superior patient comfort. Its ergonomic design allows for easy and atraumatic insertion, thereby minimizing the risk of airway trauma.</p>

<p>Primarily used in demanding clinical settings, this device benefits from <em>ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization</em>, ensuring uncompromised sterility. The Fast Track laryngeal mask offers enhanced safety and efficacy due to its strict compliance with <strong>CE</strong> standards, reflecting stringent manufacturing and testing criteria. Individually packaged, this product is ready for use and suitable for a variety of medical situations.</p>

<p>Available in <em>adjustable multi-sizes</em>, the <strong>Fast Track Laryngeal Mask</strong> adapts to different patient anatomies, providing effective sealing. This flexibility in sizes makes the device particularly versatile and indispensable for healthcare professionals seeking reliable tools tailored to each clinical need. With its <strong>ergonomic design</strong>, the mask facilitates rapid and secure intubation, solidifying its place in modern medical environments.</p>

