UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Dermatological Excision Kit', description_en = '<p>The Dermatological Excision Kit, reference KIT-DERM-001, is designed to meet the highest demands of healthcare professionals in dermatological procedures. Each kit is meticulously assembled with high-quality materials, ensuring optimal performance and enhanced safety. The primary material used, 304 Stainless Steel, is renowned for its exceptional biocompatibility, ensuring minimal interaction with skin tissues while offering remarkable strength and longevity.</p>

<p>Ethylene Oxide (EO) sterilization ensures that each component of the kit is completely free from microbial contamination, allowing for immediate and worry-free use in the operating room. Specially designed for single use, this kit guarantees a significant reduction in the risk of nosocomial infections, thus meeting the stringent standards of CE compliance.</p>

<p>Designed to be ergonomic and atraumatic, this kit includes a scalpel with a No. 15 blade, ideal for precise and controlled incisions. The 7.5 x 7.5 cm gauze pads offer high absorption capacity, essential for maintaining optimal conditions during the procedure. This product is positioned as an indispensable tool for dermatologists seeking to provide superior care to their patients.</p>

