UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Coloplast Easicath Catheter for Men (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The <strong>Coloplast Easicath Male Catheter (Multi-Sizes)</strong> is a state-of-the-art medical device designed to provide an effective and comfortable alternative for urinary catheterization. Made from high-quality <em>medical-grade silicone</em>, this product ensures <strong>exceptional biocompatibility</strong>, minimizing the risk of allergic reactions and irritation. This choice of material guarantees an enhanced user experience, focused on comfort and safety, allowing for daily use without compromising the patient''s quality of life.</p>

<p>With <strong>ethylene oxide (EO)</strong> sterilization, each catheter is carefully prepared for immediate application, meeting the strict safety standards required in today''s clinical environments. This sterilization method ensures effective pathogen elimination while preserving the integrity of the product''s material. The catheters are packaged <em>individually sterile</em>, facilitating safe and hygienic handling in various clinical situations.</p>

<p>With sizes ranging from <strong>8 to 18 CH</strong>, this device is designed to accommodate a wide range of clinical needs for men. Featuring a <em>rounded tip</em>, the catheter promotes <strong>atraumatic</strong> insertion, reducing the risk of urethral trauma. Compliance with the <strong>CE 0120</strong> standard underscores the commitment to quality and excellence, ensuring that each catheter meets European standards for medical devices. Recognized for its <strong>single-use</strong> design, this product prioritizes adherence to hygiene protocols and infection prevention.</p>

