<p>Specifically designed for professional use in clinical or hospital settings, this speculum is sterilized by ethylene oxide (EO), a process that effectively eliminates all microbial risks, thereby ensuring maximum protection and surgical safety. The individual sterile packaging enhances this safety, allowing healthcare professionals to maintain high standards of infection control during gynecological procedures.</p>

