UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Coloplast Conveen Penile Sheath (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Coloplast Conveen Penile Sheath is a medical device specifically designed for external adaptation, offering a practical solution for patients suffering from urinary incontinence. Made from natural rubber latex, this penile cone ensures optimal biocompatibility. The product design emphasizes ergonomics, allowing for a comfortable and uncompromised fit for the user. The variety of available sizes (Small, Medium, Large) caters to the specific needs of each patient, ensuring a personalized fit.</p>
<p>This device is designed for professional use, whether in a clinic or hospital environment. In accordance with CE certification, the Coloplast Conveen Penile Sheath meets safety and efficacy standards for medical use. Its individual packaging preserves its properties until the moment of use, although it is not sterile. Therefore, it is essential to rigorously follow standard hygiene procedures in clinical settings to ensure patient safety.</p>
<p>Key features of this product include an atraumatic design that minimizes the risk of skin injuries during application and removal. It is vital for practitioners to have a product that offers both reliability and ease of use to maintain a high level of care. Thanks to its specifications, the Coloplast Conveen Penile Sheath stands out as an essential choice for healthcare professionals seeking high-quality incontinence management solutions.</p>
