<p>Designed to be fully autoclavable, this laryngoscope ensures effective high-temperature sterilization, essential for preventing nosocomial infections. Each unit is packaged in an individual sterile package, ensuring a high level of purity until the moment of use. This laryngoscope is the result of advanced engineering, offering optimized visibility and ensuring precise and safe intervention with every use.</p>
