UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Pharmafix® — Soft Fabric Fixation Dressing', description_en = '<p class=''text-gray-900 text-base font-semibold''>Pharmafix® — Soft Fabric Fixation Dressing, is designed for healthcare professionals demanding a high-performance fixation solution. Made of soft non-woven fabric, this product offers optimal support while maintaining patient comfort. The biocompatibility of its hypoallergenic acrylic adhesive ensures exceptional skin tolerance, thus minimizing the risk of irritation or allergic reaction. Thanks to its ergonomic structure, Pharmafix® ensures atraumatic application, thus preserving the integrity of the patient''s skin during dressing changes.</p>

<p class=''text-gray-900 text-base font-semibold''>Compliant with European CE standards, Pharmafix® meets strict quality and safety requirements, promoting use in clinical settings. Its large size of 10 cm x 10 m allows adaptation to various anatomical surfaces, facilitating the fixation of dressings and catheters, even in hard-to-reach areas. Non-sterile, this device is ideal for general use when sterile conditions are not imperative.</p>

<p class=''text-gray-900 text-base font-semibold''>Packaged in boxes of 12 rolls, Pharmafix® ensures easy stock management and immediate availability within the hospital environment. Its lightness combined with its flexibility allows for precise and suitable handling during interventions. Moreover, its balanced adhesiveness contributes to reliable fixation without damaging the skin surface upon removal.</p>

