UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Sterile Powder-Free Disposable Latex Examination Gloves', description_en = '<p>Sterile powder-free disposable latex examination gloves are designed to meet the rigorous demands of modern clinical environments. Made from high-quality natural latex, these gloves offer remarkable biocompatibility and minimize the risk of skin allergic reactions due to their powder-free composition. Each pair is sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring a level of asepsis that complies with the strict standards of medical procedures.</p>

<p>With refined ergonomics, these one-size-fits-all gloves optimally adapt to the user''s morphology, providing a comfortable and secure fit. Their stretchability allows for precise and atraumatic movements, essential for a wide range of medical applications. The rolled cuff provides an additional barrier against accidental contamination, thereby enhancing the safety and effectiveness of personal protective equipment.</p>

<p>Fully compliant with CE certification according to EN455 standards, these gloves are designed for various clinical applications and are particularly suited for procedures where high tactile sensitivity is crucial. Packaged in boxes of 100 units, they ensure efficient and hygienic stock management in hospital settings.</p>

