UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Tracheofix Kit With Cuff (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Tracheofix Kit With Balloon is an advanced tracheal intubation solution designed to meet the rigorous demands of modern clinical interventions. Made from medical-grade polyvinyl chloride (PVC), this device ensures superior biocompatibility, reducing the risk of adverse reactions for the patient. Its design features an optimized beveled tip for atraumatic insertion, thus minimizing tissue trauma and promoting a quick and efficient intubation procedure.</p>

<p>The available sizes, ranging from 14G to 24G, offer great flexibility for a variety of clinical uses tailored to the specific needs of patients. Each kit is sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring optimal protection against infections. The device''s ergonomics are enhanced by an inflatable cuff that ensures a perfect seal, optimizing ventilation and reducing the risk of air leaks.</p>

<p>In accordance with the stringent CE standards of the European Union, the Tracheofix Kit stands out with its individual packaging. Each element of the kit is carefully sterilized and presented in easy-open packaging to facilitate quick and efficient use in emergency situations. This attention to detail and regulatory requirements underscores the commitment to safety and clinical efficacy.</p>

