UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Scalpel Blade (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The SW158511 scalpel blades, manufactured with the utmost precision from 304 stainless steel, offer exceptional performance essential for sophisticated surgical procedures. With their superior biocompatibility, these blades ensure minimal interaction with living tissues, reducing the risk of adverse reactions during surgical interventions. The sharp design of these blades allows for maximized surgical precision, facilitating clean and precise incisions, thereby reducing tissue trauma.</p>

<p>The scalpel blade is rigorously sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring that each unit is free from harmful microorganisms and ready for immediate use. Each blade is individually packaged, maintaining its sterile integrity until it is ready to be used. CE certified, these blades comply with the most stringent medical device standards, ensuring clinicians the safety and effectiveness of their instrumentation.</p>

<p>Available in various sizes ranging from 15 to 23, these single-use scalpel blades, optimized for clinical use, are ideal for precision surgeries where quality and performance must never be compromised. Their ergonomic design promotes an appealing handling, ensuring a comfortable grip during prolonged procedures. These blades are specially designed for single use, thereby reducing the risk of cross-contamination.</p>

