UPDATE product SET name_en = '1 mL Luer Slip Syringe with 27g Needle', description_en = '<p>The 1 ml Luer Slip Syringe with 27G needle is a high-precision medical device designed for demanding clinical procedures. It offers a perfect integration of functionality and biocompatibility, thus optimizing the experience for practitioners and the comfort of patients. The syringe features a Luer Slip tip that ensures a reliable and quick connection, minimizing the risk of leaks. The 1 ml capacity is ideal for precision injections, particularly in the context of clinical tests or specialized treatments.</p>

<p>The 27G gauge needle, made from medical-grade 304 stainless steel, ensures atraumatic penetration and excellent movement control, thereby reducing unpleasant sensations for the patient. Thanks to its ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization, the device maintains impeccable sterility, an essential element for infection prevention in clinical or hospital settings.</p>

<p>CE certified, this product meets strict health and safety standards, ensuring not only regulatory compliance but also peace of mind for practitioners. Suitable for professional use, this device is ergonomically designed to precisely meet the needs of specialists, ensuring smooth and efficient handling during interventions. With its notable features, the syringe ensures optimal performance and reliability that professionals can depend on.</p>

