UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Left Selective Intubation Tube Kit Ch41', description_en = '<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
    The Left Selective Intubation Tube Kit Ch41, referenced under SKU: RUS116100-000410, represents the pinnacle of modern technology in airway management. Designed to maximize the safety and efficiency of the intubation process, this kit is specifically dedicated to left lung selective intubation, offering unparalleled precision in complex surgical procedures. Its medical-grade silicone construction ensures optimal biocompatibility, reducing the risk of adverse reactions.
  </p>
  <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
    The tube has been carefully sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring impeccable sterility until opened. This meticulous sterilization process complies with the highest standards, ensuring uncompromised safety while adhering to CE certifications. This single-use product is packaged in sterile packaging, ready for use to ensure the necessary hygiene and asepsis in a hospital setting.
