UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Single-Use Flexible Ureteroscope', description_en = '<p class="font-serif text-gray-800 text-lg">The Single-Use Flexible Ureteroscope, model OTU-100RR, is a cutting-edge innovation designed for healthcare professionals specializing in urological interventions. Made from medical-grade polyurethane, this product offers superior biocompatibility, ensuring patient safety and comfort during delicate endourological procedures. The device is designed for single use, thereby eliminating any risk of cross-contamination, underscoring the commitment to a high standard of hygienic practice.</p>
<p class="mt-4 font-serif text-gray-800 text-lg">Its compact dimensions, 5 Fr in diameter with a length of 600 mm, allow for easy handling and precise penetration, effectively reaching targeted areas within the urinary tract. Equipped with a flexible and atraumatic tip, it ensures smooth passage, minimizing discomfort for the patient and thus optimizing procedural outcomes. The ergonomics have been carefully studied to offer optimal maneuverability, allowing clinicians to navigate with precision and confidence.</p>
<p class="mt-4 font-serif text-gray-800 text-lg">This device is sterilized using ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring complete disinfection. Compliant with stringent CE standards, it results from a robust manufacturing process adhering to high levels of quality and reliability. This sterile medical instrument is individually packaged, ensuring its sterility until the moment of use. The Single-Use Flexible Ureteroscope presents itself as an essential tool in the arsenal of solutions offered by urology specialists for safe and effective interventions.</p>
