UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Coloplast Easicath Catheter for Women (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Coloplast Easicath Female Urinary Catheter (Multi-Sizes) is designed to provide an atraumatic, effective, and ergonomic solution for intermittent urinary catheterization in women. Crafted with meticulous attention to biocompatibility, this medical device relies on medical-grade PVC material, free from phthalates, to ensure optimal safety and reduce the risk of tissue irritation.</p><p>Thanks to its ethylene oxide sterilization process, the catheter ensures a high level of sterility, essential for preventing nosocomial infections. Its rounded hydrophilic tip design promotes an atraumatic passage through the urethra, thus minimizing discomfort associated with the procedure. This product, designed for single use, ensures patient safety while adhering to the rigorous standards of CE certification.</p><p>With dimensions ranging from 6 to 12 CH, the Coloplast Easicath Female Catheter is designed for adaptability and patient comfort, facilitating use in both hospital settings and home care. Its individual sterile packaging minimizes the risk of cross-contamination while preserving the product''s integrity until use.</p><p>This product embodies Coloplast''s commitment to providing innovative healthcare solutions that meet international clinical and regulatory requirements, offering healthcare professionals the confidence needed for quality care.</p><table class="min-w-full leading-normal"><thead><tr><th class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-100 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase">Specification</th><th class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-100 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase">Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Material</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Medical-grade PVC, phthalate-free</td></tr><tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Sterilization</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Ethylene Oxide (EO)</td></tr><tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Compliance</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">CE Certification</td></tr><tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Clinical Use</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Single use</td></tr><tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Features</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm">Rounded hydrophilic tip, individual sterile packaging, dimensions from 6 to 12 CH</td></tr></tbody></table>' WHERE id = 516;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Standard Suture Kit (Complete)', description_en = '<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">The Standard Suture Kit (Complete) is designed to meet the requirements of minor clinical procedures, offering high-quality tools to ensure safe and effective results. Made from 304 stainless steel, this kit boasts exceptional biocompatibility and corrosion resistance, ensuring optimal durability even with frequent use. Each instrument is ergonomically designed for prolonged comfort, thus minimizing practitioner fatigue during delicate procedures.</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">Ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization ensures the kit achieves a high level of sterility, essential for preventing any risk of cross-contamination. The sterile individual packaging preserves the integrity of each instrument until use. The kit includes essential tools, such as a 12 cm dissecting forceps, a 14 cm needle holder, and 11 cm IRIS scissors, each designed to perform its function with efficient and atraumatic precision.</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">Compliant with CE and ISO 13485 standards, this kit ensures unmatched quality and safety, thus meeting the rigorous standards of the modern medical environment. The selection of instruments and manufacturing methodology are optimized to facilitate medical procedures while reducing potential postoperative complications.</p>

