</div>' WHERE id = 526;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Catheter Mount (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Catheter Mount (Multi-Sizes) SKU: RUS191014-000200 is designed to meet the most demanding expectations of healthcare professionals in terms of clinical performance and patient safety. Made from medical-grade silicone, it ensures optimal biocompatibility, thereby reducing the risk of immune reaction or irritation in the patient. The silicone used offers exceptional flexibility that guarantees atraumatic passage and secure insertion, minimizing discomfort and tissue trauma.</p>
<p>Ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization ensures total asepsis, making this product ready for use immediately after opening. Each unit is carefully packaged in an individual sterile package to maintain this condition until use, thus ensuring maximum protection against contamination. Available in various sizes from 14G to 22G, this catheter mount is suitable for a wide range of clinical applications, from standard infusions to precision sampling.</p>
<p>CE certified, the Catheter Mount complies with the strictest standards of the medical industry, attesting to its quality and safety in clinical use. Additionally, its carefully designed beveled tip allows for smooth and uniform penetration, reducing potential trauma during insertion. Its ergonomic design facilitates handling by nursing and medical staff, thereby increasing operational efficiency. This product is intended for single professional use, ensuring safe and effective medical practices.</p>
