UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Non-Balloon Endotracheal Tube (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Non-Cuffed Intubation Tube (Multi-Sizes) is designed to offer superior performance during tracheal intubation procedures. Made from premium medical-grade silicone, this tube ensures exceptional biocompatibility, thereby reducing the risk of adverse responses in sensitive mucosal tissue. Its robust construction ensures easy handling while providing optimal flexibility that anatomically adapts to the patient.</p>

<p>Each tube is sterilized using ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring purity and clinical safety. The EO sterilization technique is well recognized for maintaining material integrity while effectively eliminating microbiological contamination. Intended for single use, the tube guarantees high hygiene standards and minimizes the risk of cross-infections.</p>

<p>Equipped with an atraumatic rounded tip, this tube reduces trauma during insertion, thereby contributing to increased patient comfort. The length ranging from 200 to 300 mm allows for a wide range of clinical applications, meeting the varied needs of healthcare professionals in intubation. CE compliance certifies that this device meets essential safety and performance requirements. Each is individually packaged and sterile, ensuring aseptic handling up to the point of use.</p>

