<td class="border-t border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Atraumatic rounded tip, length 200-300 mm, individual sterile packaging</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table><p>This medical device is designed with high clinical quality materials. Key technical features: <strong>Material</strong>: Transparent thermosensitive medical PVC. <strong>Cuff</strong>: None (Ideal for strict pediatric use). <strong>Bevel</strong>: Atraumatic Murphy type. <strong>Marking</strong>: Clear insertion graduations (cm). <strong>Clinical Use</strong>: Neonatal/pediatric short-term intubation. </p>' WHERE id = 23;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Tracheofix Kit Without Cuff (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Tracheofix Kit Without Cuff (Multi-Sizes) is an advanced care solution designed to provide healthcare professionals with optimal performance in clinical or hospital settings. This device is distinguished by the use of high-quality polyurethane material, ensuring exceptional biocompatibility and long-term durability. Thanks to its multi-size design, it easily adapts to a wide variety of patients, ensuring increased comfort and safety during use.</p>

<p>Ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization ensures the product''s purity and microbiological safety, effectively preventing nosocomial infections. Fully compliant with CE standards and recognized for its reliability, the Tracheofix Kit Without Cuff simplifies clinical processes with its individual sterile packaging, thus minimizing the risk of cross-contamination.</p>

<p>The ergonomic features of the device, including its atraumatic blunt tip, allow for gentle and trauma-free insertion for the patient, reducing the risk of complications. This technical innovation reflects our engineers'' dedication to developing medical instruments that meet the rigorous demands of modern practitioners.</p>

