UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Laryngoscope with Blades – Cullinan (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Laryngoscope with Blades - Cullinan (Multi-Sizes), reference HUGVL4R432, is a high-class medical device designed for healthcare professionals demanding reliability and performance. Made from 304 stainless steel, this laryngoscope ensures optimal biocompatibility and exceptional durability, even in the most demanding clinical environments. The 304 stainless steel provides resistance to both wear and corrosion, offering a long-lasting solution for airway visualization.</p>

<p>This device is sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), a method recognized for its effectiveness in eliminating all microorganisms, thus ensuring maximum safety and hygiene. CE certified, this laryngoscope meets the strictest quality and safety standards, guaranteeing practitioners confident use in their daily procedures.</p>

<p>Available in multiple interchangeable sizes (4/3/2, 00/0/1, 5/4/1), this precision instrument offers ergonomic and adaptable features that maximize user comfort. Its atraumatic design reduces the risk of soft tissue injury, while the individual box packaging facilitates transport and storage. Versatile and efficient, the Cullinan laryngoscope is an essential tool in the current arsenal of instruments for anesthesia and emergency.</p>

