UPDATE product SET name_en = 'General Practitioner Consultation Kit', description_en = '<p>The General Practitioner Consultation Kit, SKU: KIT-GEN-001, is designed to meet the essential needs of healthcare professionals during medical consultations. This kit, reflecting a commitment to quality and safety, includes components carefully selected for their durability, biocompatibility, and compliance with the highest clinical standards.</p><p>The beech wood tongue depressors, chosen for their robustness and allergen neutrality, ensure atraumatic and safe use during oral examinations. The powder-free nitrile gloves are medium-sized, providing excellent ergonomics and optimal comfort for the user, while offering chemical resistance and protection against infectious agents. These gloves meet the expectations of flexibility and tactile sensitivity required in a medical environment.</p><p>The Type IIR masks, compliant with the EN 14683:2019 standard, provide reliable protection against particles and pathogens during procedures. Their design offers high breathability without compromising safety. To complete this kit, the 500 ml hand sanitizer gel, containing 70% ethanol, ensures effective and rapid hand disinfection, in line with hospital hygiene recommendations.</p><table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200"><thead class="bg-gray-50"><tr><th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Specification</th><th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200"><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Tongue Depressor Material</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Beech wood</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Glove Material</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Powder-free nitrile</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Glove Size</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Medium</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Mask Type</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Type IIR</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Mask Standard</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">EN 14683:2019</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Hand Sanitizer Volume</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">500 ml</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Alcohol Concentration in Gel</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">70% ethanol</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Sterilization</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Not applicable</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">CE Compliance</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Yes, to current clinical standards</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Clinical Use</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">General consultation</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Features</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">Biocompatibility, high durability, ergonomics, optimal protection</td></tr></tbody></table>' WHERE id = 10002;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Guedel Airway (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Guedel Airway (Multi-Sizes), referenced under SKU RUS124900-000001, is an advancement in the field of clinical respiratory support. Designed to provide optimal support during the administration of respiratory care, this medical device is essential in modern clinics and hospitals. Made from high-quality medical-grade plastic, the airway ensures maximum biocompatibility with human tissues, thus ensuring safe use.</p>

<p>Thanks to its ergonomic design, the airway integrates seamlessly into medical interventions, allowing for safe and effective intubation with its open tip. The variety of sizes, ranging from 00 to 6, ensures a perfect fit for every morphology, thereby reducing complications and enhancing patient comfort. The ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization process guarantees a product ready for use while ensuring its long-term sterility.</p>

<p>CE certified for medical devices, the Guedel Airway complies with the most stringent standards in terms of safety and performance. Each airway is individually packaged to preserve its sterility until use. This individual packaging also facilitates storage and handling while minimizing the risk of cross-contamination.</p>

