UPDATE product SET name_en = '1 mL Insulin Syringe with Fixed 29g Needle', description_en = '<p>The 1 ml insulin syringe with a fixed 29G needle, referenced under SKU: NEO176501/29, is a high-precision medical device designed to ensure safe and effective insulin administration. Its precise one-milliliter capacity is ideal for applications requiring exact dosing, thus ensuring optimized insulin therapy management. The 29G gauge needle, made of surgical-grade stainless steel, features an atraumatic tip to minimize patient discomfort while ensuring smooth and precise penetration.</p>

<p>In terms of biocompatibility, this product is sterilized by ethylene oxide (EO), offering a high level of sterility in compliance with international safety standards. The syringe barrel is made of transparent polypropylene to allow good visibility of the contents, thus facilitating correct and precise insulin administration. The device''s ergonomics are optimized for a secure and comfortable grip, enabling healthcare professionals to perform injections with ease and confidence.</p>

<p>This device is CE certified, attesting to its compliance with regulatory safety and performance requirements. Intended for single use, it ensures adherence to hygiene protocols and prevents the risk of cross-contamination. Each syringe is individually packaged in a sterile manner, thus guaranteeing maximum integrity until the moment of use. This insulin syringe is specifically intended for clinical use, meeting the needs of healthcare professionals involved in the daily care of diabetic patients.</p>

