UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Coloplast Urostomy Bag 1-Piece Pediatric Alterna Transparent', description_en = '<p>The Coloplast Uro Pouch 1 Piece Child Alterna Transp is a high-quality urinary pouch solution dedicated to pediatric use. Made from medical-grade silicone, this pouch offers optimal biocompatibility, ensuring atraumatic and safe contact with children''s delicate skin. Its transparency allows for easy and continuous monitoring, thus ensuring effective clinical follow-up.</p>

<p>Designed with children''s ergonomics in mind, this pouch is lightweight and can be worn discreetly under clothing. Although non-sterile, it complies with stringent CE standards, ensuring superior safety and uncompromised reliability. With a capacity of 120 ml, it is ideal for meeting the specific needs of the pediatric population.</p>

<p>One of the key features of this product is its practicality. The packaging in a box of 20 units aims to facilitate stock management and ensure that a clean solution is always at hand. These pouches are ideal for daily use and recommended by healthcare professionals for their proven performance and design that respects infant physiology.</p>

