UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Luer Slip Syringe 3-Piece (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Luer Slip 3-Piece Syringe (Multi-Sizes) SKU: NEO176550SLIP is designed to meet the highest standards of the medical sector. Made from medical-grade polypropylene, it offers superior biocompatibility, ensuring safety and reliability when used in clinical settings. Its three-piece design ensures precise control of the injected medication while minimizing the risk of leakage or spillage. The perfect transparency of the syringe barrel allows for optimal visual control of the contents, thus facilitating its use by healthcare practitioners.</p>

<p>Sterilized by ethylene oxide (EO), each syringe is individually packaged to ensure maximum sterility until use. The Luer Slip tip type allows for quick and secure connection with a variety of medical accessories, while facilitating the medication administration process. The atraumatic design principle is integrated to ensure optimal patient comfort.</p>

<p>This product is CE certified, synonymous with compliance with the most stringent quality and safety standards. The syringes are designed for single use, reducing the risk of cross-contamination and adhering to best clinical practices. They are available in multiple capacities – 2 ml, 5 ml, 10 ml, and 20 ml – thus offering a flexible solution suitable for different medical needs.</p>

