UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Wiscope Flexible Single-Use Flexible Cystoscope', description_en = '<p>The Single Use Flexible Cystoscope Wiscope, SKU: OTU-C380RR, is a state-of-the-art medical device designed to provide an optimal clinical experience through its advanced engineering and highest quality materials. Made with 304 Stainless Steel, known for its exceptional biocompatibility and effective resistance to all forms of corrosion, this cystoscope ensures reliable performance. Its single-use nature eliminates the risk of cross-infections, thereby guaranteeing maximum patient safety.</p><p>This cystoscope features a flexible tip, which helps minimize trauma during delicate and sensitive endoscopic procedures. The flexibility of the tip enhances ergonomics and allows for smoother and atraumatic insertion, increasing patient comfort while maintaining excellent visibility for the clinician. The sterile individual packaging, thanks to ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization, ensures that each unit is ready to be used directly from the package, offering substantial time savings in dynamic care environments.</p><p>The Wiscope is certified to comply with CE standards, ensuring it meets rigorous European safety and performance standards. Its compact dimensions, 3.5 mm by 40 cm, make it suitable for a variety of clinical applications, allowing adaptation in diverse operating environments. Its design is specifically oriented towards single use, making it not only easy to manage but also economical in terms of use and maintenance.</p><table class="w-full text-left border-collapse"><thead><tr><th class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Specification</th><th class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-t border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Material</td><td class="border-t border-b border-gray-300 py-2">304 Stainless Steel</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Sterilization</td><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Ethylene Oxide (EO)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">CE / ISO Compliance</td><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">CE Certification</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Clinical Use</td><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Single use, atraumatic endoscopies</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Features</td><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Diameter 3.5 mm x Length 40 cm, Flexible tip, Ergonomic use</td></tr></tbody></table>' WHERE id = 531;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Gynecological Examination Kit', description_en = '<p>The Gynecological Examination Kit (SKU: KIT-GYN-001) represents a remarkable advancement in clinical gynecological practice thanks to its ergonomic design intended to facilitate diagnostic and therapeutic procedures. Made from high-quality medical plastic, this kit ensures exceptional biocompatibility, thereby reducing the risk of adverse reactions for the patient. Each component is designed to offer maximum comfort to the practitioner while ensuring an atraumatic experience for the patient.</p><p>The sterility of the kit is ensured by ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization, a reliable process that ensures the complete elimination of microorganisms, adhering to the highest health safety standards. The speculum, with a standard medium size, is ideal for the majority of patients and is designed for single use to prevent cross-contamination and ensure optimal infection control.</p><p>The kit is carefully packaged in an individual sterile package, facilitating handling and preserving its sterility until the moment of use. The brush included in the kit features a soft tip with a nylon end, ideal for homogeneous sample collection without epithelial cell disruption. Compliant with CE 0123 certification, this kit meets regulatory requirements and ensures safe and effective use in clinical settings.</p><table class="w-full border-collapse"><thead><tr><th class="border-b py-2 px-4 text-left">Specification</th><th class="border-b py-2 px-4 text-left">Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Material</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Medical plastic</td></tr><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Sterilization</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Ethylene oxide (EO)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">CE / ISO Compliance</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">CE 0123</td></tr><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Clinical Use</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Single use</td></tr><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Features</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Medium-sized speculum, Individual sterile packaging, Soft nylon brush tip</td></tr></tbody></table>' WHERE id = 10003;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Urinary Catheterization Kit', description_en = '<p>The Urinary Catheterization Kit, model KIT-URO-001, is designed to provide a premium medical solution for healthcare professionals requiring atraumatic and efficient bladder management. This kit is meticulously manufactured to ensure a safe and comfortable experience for patients. The catheter is made of soft silicone, a material known for its high biocompatibility and optimal comfort during prolonged insertion. This material choice significantly reduces the risk of allergies and irritation, ensuring prolonged use without complications.</p>

<p>The ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization process ensures complete elimination of microorganisms, offering maximum safety for medical procedures. The 2-liter collection bag capacity is ideal for effective drainage management, while minimizing the need for frequent emptying. Additionally, the kit includes a 10 ml syringe, which allows precise and controlled adjustment of the catheter''s state in the patient''s bladder, thus providing essential therapeutic flexibility for caregivers.</p>

<p>Equipped with a water-based anesthetic gel lubricant, this kit offers carefully designed lubrication for easy insertion and removal, minimizing patient discomfort. The 2-way Foley catheter design enhances urinary flow and facilitates irrigation, ideal for both short and long-term applications. Each kit is individually packaged in a sterile manner, providing peace of mind for both medical staff and patients, ensuring product integrity until application. Compliant with international CE and ISO standards, the KIT-URO-001 represents excellence in clinical innovations.</p>

