UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Right Selective Intubation Catheter Kit Ch39', description_en = '<p>The <strong>Right Selective Intubation Tube Kit Ch39</strong> is a highly innovative medical device designed to provide a reliable solution for selective intubation in demanding clinical environments. Made from <span class=''text-gray-700''>premium medical-grade PVC</span>, this device ensures exceptional biocompatibility and optimal patient comfort, while guaranteeing robust resistance essential for safe interventions.</p>

<p>The device has undergone rigorous ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization, certified for microbial efficacy, ensuring its immediate suitability for clinical use. The CE certification attests to its compliance with current safety and performance standards, positioning the product at the pinnacle of medical industry standards.</p>

<p>Characterized by a length of 39 cm and a diameter of 6 mm, the kit is specially designed for right pulmonary selective intubation. Its innovative beveled tip makes insertion atraumatic, thus facilitating an ergonomic approach and reducing the risk of complications during the intubation process. Each unit is carefully packaged in an individual sterile package, ensuring its integrity until the point of use.</p>

