UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Wiscope 7.5 Fr Single-Use Flexible Ureteroscope', description_en = '<p>The Wiscope 7.5 Fr Single-Use Flexible Ureteroscope is designed to meet the highest clinical demands, offering optimal flexibility and maneuverability for urological procedures. With a size of 7.5 Fr, this ureteroscope is perfectly suited for atraumatic interventions requiring high precision. The biocompatibility of polyurethane ensures safe contact with body tissues, minimizing the risk of adverse reactions and maximizing patient comfort.</p>

<p>Compliant with CE standards, this medical device meets internationally recognized rigorous safety and performance criteria. Its single-use design eliminates the risk of cross-contamination, ensuring impeccable hygiene with each use. Individually packaged and sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), each device is ready for use immediately after opening, thus optimizing workflow in high-paced clinical environments.</p>

<p>The advanced ergonomics of this flexible ureteroscope ensure easy handling, even in complex clinical situations. Thanks to its lightweight construction and optimized force installation, healthcare professionals can focus more on the intervention and less on the equipment. In summary, the Wiscope 7.5 Fr offers a superior quality solution for the exploration and treatment of urinary tracts, perfectly suited for institutions committed to providing excellent care.</p>

