    <p>With a 1080p HD camera resolution, the system provides superior image quality, allowing clinicians to differentiate even the most subtle anatomical structures, thereby optimizing diagnostic efficiency. Its ergonomics, combined with an atraumatic design, reduce operator fatigue and potential tissue trauma during insertion and manipulation.</p>
    <p>In compliance with the strictest safety standards, the Imaging System is CE certified and sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring the highest levels of hygiene. The USB-C connection simplifies integration with modern digital systems for an efficient workflow. These features make this ureteroscope an essential component of advanced medical equipment.</p>
