UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Nasal Speculum (Greatcare) (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Greatcare Nasal Speculum is designed to meet the rigorous demands of modern clinical and hospital environments with its high-quality 304 stainless steel construction. This material is renowned for its exceptional biocompatibility, ensuring an inert interaction with biological tissues and reducing the risk of allergic or inflammatory reactions in patients. The speculum''s design incorporates an ergonomic mechanism that facilitates handling by healthcare professionals, ensuring both safe and effective use.</p>
<p>The Nasal Speculum is sterilized by Ethylene Oxide (EO), providing the medical device with a superior level of microbiological safety, essential in preventing nosocomial infections. With its rounded edges, this speculum offers atraumatic performance, thus minimizing the risk of injury to delicate nasal tissues during examinations or procedures.</p>
<p>Available in multiple sizes, this product is CE certified, ensuring its compliance with strict European standards for medical devices. Each unit is individually packaged in a sterile manner, guaranteeing optimal hygiene until the moment of use. Intended for professional use in clinics and hospitals, the Greatcare Nasal Speculum is an indispensable tool for professionals seeking to provide high-quality and safe care.</p>

